### ============================================================
###   Notification Service — Event-Driven (No REST Endpoints)
### ============================================================
### This service is purely event-driven and does NOT expose
### REST API endpoints. It consumes Kafka events and processes
### notifications (email/SMS simulation via logging).
###
### Kafka Topics Consumed:
###   - order-events  (consumer group: notification-group)
###   - payment-events (consumer group: notification-group)
###
### To test, create an order through the Order Service which
### triggers the full event chain:
###   Order Created → Payment Processed → Notification Sent
### ============================================================

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8087/actuator/health

###

### 2. Service Info
GET http://localhost:8087/actuator/info

###

### 3. Prometheus Metrics (for monitoring)
GET http://localhost:8087/actuator/prometheus

###
